text: Ghoshal is an Indian surname. Notable people with this surname include: * Nandini Ghosal, Indian dancer * Soukarya Ghosal (born 1986), Indian film director, lyricist, animator and screenplay writer * Saurav Ghosal (born 1986), Indian squash player * Shreya Ghoshal , Indian singer ==See also== * Ghoshal (disambiguation)
title: Ghosal
